{"tid":789056,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"童年回憶VS原地踏步-玩Fifa同PES既你入一入黎","createTime":"2018-08-22T03:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T11:13:49.000Z","uid":72649,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2677fd8a5d57a83d3dd0557e61f44a805047130b","tid":789056,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:18:35.000Z","msg":"中學時代PS2玩WE 印象中好似最後係2012, 去到PS3開始因爲pro club轉玩Fifa<br />\n但Fifa感覺越出越唔好玩，操控感畫質根本一成不變，近代比較有突破既就係得L2食位。my story同今集咩FIFA street 元素就係啲gimmick野，個射門時機系統有待商榷啦。反而最基本既就毫無進步，應該有個啲就冇埋 e.g online friendliness 2v2系統, career mode 玩國家隊冇得幫球員轉號碼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2ODA0lwSIGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2ODA0lwSIGk&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=2f0825d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2ODA0lwSIGk</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試玩左PES2019，玩落似係踢翻真既足球(球員唔會好似機械人咁下下完美控球)，而且個畫質球員養真係靚得好誇張。感覺上Konami相比EA有誠意好多，但PES最大既負面考量始終係license問題，玩落用假衫假名單身鞋仔感覺有啲差<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j02R8epZGYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj02R8epZGYA&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=dd1efac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j02R8epZGYA</a><br />\n<br />\n想問下玩開PES既巴打有冇方法好似PS2以前咁抄save用真波衫，有既話online mode又用唔用到？<br />\n而玩開FIFA既巴打又會唔會考慮轉玩PES, FIFA今集有中招好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pXK24GlrgIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpXK24GlrgIg&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=ff6b65b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pXK24GlrgIg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kkp9Z2U7O8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKkp9Z2U7O8w&d=PHxlR1nZkxZlRZVXiLssDWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=be41d6fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kkp9Z2U7O8w</a><br />\n<br />\n加上人大左，放左工冇咁多時間打機，都唔會咁有心機去煲去課金UT,玩wl 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a4d49f8d4c8da6d7598659ee5ae02792c1090f","tid":789056,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"翻梗工打<br />\n<br />\n好多錯別字<br />\n<br />\n得啲gimmick野<br />\n中超"},{"pid":"de2e4181c3085e13e9f2ab25f0a42ccbacf853ba","tid":789056,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},{"pid":"bfe866ce52e6db16030640eb6f6a3bb898b9580e","tid":789056,"uid":133266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:23:25.000Z","msg":"算啦 大部分人咪又係爲左fut同pro club買哂fifa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5a14fad08dac35864973238771d26a90c97c58","tid":789056,"uid":32059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"license 都算係一個幾重要既問題，除非2者都有相同既資源之下去做一個競爭，如果唔係冇得去比較...一定會係fifa佔大比數"},{"pid":"6fc9ddcb37298b700ee162ea648b09667a035d4e","tid":789056,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de2e4181c3085e13e9f2ab25f0a42ccbacf853ba","tid":789056,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:21:23.000Z","msg":"打手味濃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:33:30.000Z","msg":"真金白銀自己俾錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係冇錢先問下買邊隻好，時間金錢只容許二揀一"},{"pid":"31e1df5449ddffe8dcf76f406ee6e93ba891aca4","tid":789056,"uid":72649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f5a14fad08dac35864973238771d26a90c97c58","tid":789056,"uid":32059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"license 都算係一個幾重要既問題，除非2者都有相同既資源之下去做一個競爭，如果唔係冇得去比較...一定會係fifa佔大比數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:35:23.000Z","msg":"但gameplay好似PES追翻上黎<br />\n畫質就不嬲都唔洗講<im